    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2118230/extras/5b7bbacfcdad02b63c641c58f6c7b4f1.avif?t=1769713836\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build and battle against an army of the undead as you attempt to kill Death itself. Grow your undead army overtime and develop your graveyard with traps and towers to survive as long as possible.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >💀 Create Your Own Synergies!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2118230/extras/8f1e419122e76cdb097f8e8607793931.poster.avif?t=1769713836\" width=800 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2118230/extras/8f1e419122e76cdb097f8e8607793931.webm?t=1769713836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2118230/extras/8f1e419122e76cdb097f8e8607793931.mp4?t=1769713836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >📜 Features<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Develop a Huge Army of 100 Total Units!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Place Structures to Bolster Your Army</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Cast Fireballs, Lightning Strikes and Poison Bombs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Fight a Giant Boss and Their Army</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Earn Achievements </p></li></ul></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🤝 Community Focused Development</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I want your help to make NecroTactics better so if you want to be a part of the testing and give me feedback you can reach me (Jerome) on Discord. Thank you to everyone who has supported the development of my past games as you have made this game possible!</p>",
